sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Purchase as Purchase Orchestrator
    participant SeatInv as Seat Inventory gRPC
    participant Postgres as PostgreSQL

    Purchase->>SeatInv: HoldSeat(inventoryId, userId)
    loop up to MAX_DEADLOCK_RETRIES
        SeatInv->>Postgres: SELECT ... FOR UPDATE + update seat row
        alt deadlock detected
            Postgres-->>SeatInv: 40P01 deadlock
            SeatInv->>SeatInv: exponential backoff + jitter
        else lock succeeds
            Postgres-->>SeatInv: row updated to held
            SeatInv-->>Purchase: success + holdToken
        end
    end
    alt retries exhausted
        SeatInv-->>Purchase: DEADLOCK_FAILED
    end
